title: B.S. Report - Alex Morgan & Abby Wambach
description: Bill visits Abby Wambach and Alex Morgan as they train for the World Cup to discuss the evolution of women's soccer, how playing many sports at a young age helped them excel in soccer, and what you can do to help them bring the World Cup home.
